(7338,'Move along, rube.','',10038,0,10,0,1,0,0,0,0,'This ain\'t a ride, clem.  Beat it.','',10039,0,10,0,1,0,0,0,0,'If you\'re trying to be friendly, save your breath.  Better yet, just stop breathing all together.','',10040,0,6,0,1,0,0,0,0,'In case it wasn\'t obvious, I\'m not here for customer relations.','',10041,0,6,0,1,0,0,0,0,'You mess with Silas, you mess with me.  Have a nice day.','',10042,0,10,0,1,0,0,0,0,'I need a second head like I need to lose my first one.','',10043,0,1,0,1,0,0,0,0,'I lived in Dire Maul for a little bit.  That was fun.  Really.','',10044,0,1,0,1,0,0,0,0,'Unlike most ogres, I do know what an outhouse is for - giving you a swirlie.  Now beat it.','',10045,0,1,0,1,0,0,0,0,11723),
